   Bjornir is an elderly man, who appears well passed his days of battle.  He
appears to be angry as a default emotion, perhaps thinking his death might be
in his armory, and not in battle as he probably expected.  He is wearing a
light leather jerkin and some loose-fitting dark pants.  He looks as if he
would attack anyone who thought to touch the items in the armory.  His long,
silver hair is held back with a leather tie and he watches everything closely
with piercing near-black irises.  
~
