#31407
Rollo Jarl man~
Jarl Rollo~
A muscular man wearing the full hide of a bear glares at you from under the upper jaw of the bear.
~
   Rollo is the Jarl of the Stronghold and the leader of the Norseman in this
area.  He appears to be over 7 foot tall and is proportionally wide.  He is
wearing leather pants and a cloak embroidered in red Nordic runes.  His
clothing alone indicates his high stature and the air of authority he projects
only strengthens that notion.  His movements are practiced and the sheer power
that he wields is apparent.  He could only become more powerful if he were to
be wielding a weapon in his giant hands.  
~
